-- ══════════════════════════════════════
--  Rain Hub — Updates:
--  • Replaced "Shoot Murd" with Auto Farm
--    – Noclips player through all parts
--    – Tweens to nearest Coin_Server parts
--    – Auto re-targets on despawn
--    – Rainbow animated ESP on all coins
--  • ESP now shows rainbow glow on
--    Coin_Server parts for debugging
